article.description: — Idan Tretout's 34 points led Iona over Sacred Heart 88-81 on Friday night.
article.headline: Tretout scores 34, Iona downs Sacred Heart 88-81
article.linkText: Tretout scores 34, Iona downs Sacred Heart 88-81
article.story: NEW ROCHELLE, N.Y. -- — Idan Tretout's 34 points led Iona over Sacred Heart 88-81 on Friday night. Tretout was 12 of 21 shooting, including 7 for 12 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 9 from the line for the Gaels (1-1). Wheza Panzo finished 4 of 10 from 3-point range to add 12 points. Joel Brown was 4 of 7 shooting and 1 of 4 from the free throw line to finish with 10 points, while adding seven rebounds, five assists, and five steals. Nico Galette led the way for the Pioneers (1-1) with 20 points, 10 rebounds, four assists and four steals. Sacred Heart also got 17 points and seven rebounds from Tanner Thomas. Aidan Carpenter also had 14 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
